# Business Flow Diagrams

## Main Application Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([App Launch]) --> Tray[Create System Tray]
    Tray --> Shortcuts[Register Global Shortcuts]
    Shortcuts --> Hidden[Hide Main Window]
    Hidden --> Wait[Wait for User Input]

    Wait -->|Alt+Space| Toggle{Window Visible?}
    Toggle -->|Yes| Hide[Hide Window]
    Toggle -->|No| Show[Show + Focus Window]
    Hide --> Wait
    Show --> Wait

    Wait -->|Alt+S| Screenshot[Open Selector<br/>Screenshot Mode]
    Wait -->|Alt+O| OCR[Open Selector<br/>OCR Mode]

    Screenshot --> Select[User Selects Region]
    OCR --> Select
    Select --> Capture[Capture Screen]
    Capture --> Mode{Mode?}
    Mode -->|screenshot| OpenImage[Open Image File]
    Mode -->|ocr| MockOCR[Mock OCR<br/>Copy to Clipboard]
    OpenImage --> Wait
    MockOCR --> Wait

    Wait -->|Tray Click| Toggle
    Wait -->|Quit| Exit([Exit App])
```

## Search Flow

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    Start([User Types]) --> Debounce[Debounce 50ms]
    Debounce --> Parallel[Query All Plugins]

    Parallel --> AppLauncher[App Launcher]
    Parallel --> Calculator[Calculator]
    Parallel --> Docker[Docker]
    Parallel --> WebSearch[Web Search]

    AppLauncher --> Filter1{Matches?}
    Calculator --> Filter2{Valid Math?}
    Docker --> Filter3{Matches?}
    WebSearch --> Filter4{Always}

    Filter1 -->|Yes| Results1[App Results]
    Filter1 -->|No| Empty1[Skip]
    Filter2 -->|Yes| Results2[Calc Result]
    Filter2 -->|No| Empty2[Skip]
    Filter3 -->|Yes| Results3[Docker Results]
    Filter3 -->|No| Empty3[Skip]
    Filter4 --> Results4[Search Link]

    Results1 --> Flatten[Flatten + Sort]
    Results2 --> Flatten
    Results3 --> Flatten
    Results4 --> Flatten
    Empty1 --> Flatten
    Empty2 --> Flatten
    Empty3 --> Flatten

    Flatten --> Render[Render List]
    Render --> Navigate[Arrow Keys Navigate]
    Navigate --> Enter[Enter to Select]
    Enter --> Action[Execute onSelect]
```

## Chat Flow (Current / Mocked)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([Enter Chat]) --> View[Switch to Chat View]
    View --> Input[User Types Message]
    Input --> Send[Press Enter]
    Send --> AddUser[Add User Message<br/>to State]
    AddUser --> Render1[Render User Bubble]
    Render1 --> Wait[Wait 600ms]
    Wait --> Mock[Generate Mock Response]
    Mock --> AddAssistant[Add Assistant Message<br/>to State]
    AddAssistant --> Render2[Render Assistant Bubble]
    Render2 --> More{More Messages?}
    More -->|Yes| Input
    More -->|No| End([End])
```

## Settings Configuration Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([Open Settings]) --> Load[Load from localStorage]
    Load --> Render[Render Form]

    Render --> OAuth[OAuth Section]
    OAuth --> ClickOAuth[Click Provider]
    ClickOAuth --> Toggle{Already Connected?}
    Toggle -->|Yes| Disconnect[Set authProvider to null]
    Toggle -->|No| Connect[Set authProvider to ID]
    Disconnect --> Render
    Connect --> Render

    Render --> APIKey[API Key Section]
    APIKey --> SelectProvider[Select Provider]
    SelectProvider --> Render
    APIKey --> EnterKey[Enter API Key]
    EnterKey --> Render
    APIKey --> ToggleVisibility[Toggle Show/Hide]
    ToggleVisibility --> Render

    Render --> OCR[OCR Model Section]
    OCR --> SelectModel[Select Model]
    SelectModel --> Render

    Render --> Save[Click Save]
    Save --> Persist[Save to localStorage]
    Persist --> Close[Close Settings]
    Close --> End([Return to Search])

    Render --> Cancel[Click Cancel]
    Cancel --> End
```

## Region Selection Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([Trigger Alt+S/O]) --> Create[Create/Show Selector Window]
    Create --> Fullscreen[Fullscreen Transparent Overlay]
    Fullscreen --> Wait[Wait for Mouse Input]

    Wait -->|Mouse Down| StartDrag[Record Start Position]
    StartDrag --> Dragging[Mouse Move]
    Dragging --> Update[Update Current Position]
    Update --> Draw[Draw Selection Rectangle]
    Draw --> Dragging

    Dragging -->|Mouse Up| EndDrag[Calculate Bounds]
    EndDrag --> Valid{Width > 2 &&<br/>Height > 2?}
    Valid -->|Yes| Capture[Invoke capture_region]
    Valid -->|No| Reset[Reset Selection]
    Reset --> Wait

    Capture --> Rust[Rust Backend Processes]
    Rust --> Hide[Hide Selector]
    Hide --> Delay[Wait 150ms]
    Delay --> ScreenCap[Capture Screen]
    ScreenCap --> Crop[Crop Region]
    Crop --> Save[Save to Desktop]

    Save --> Mode{Mode?}
    Mode -->|screenshot| Open[Open in Viewer]
    Mode -->|ocr| OCRText[Mock OCR Text]
    OCRText --> Clipboard[Copy to Clipboard]

    Open --> Close[Close Selector]
    Clipboard --> Close
    Close --> End([Done])

    Wait -->|Escape| Cancel[Close Selector]
    Cancel --> End
```

## Docker Management Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([Type "docker"]) --> Query[Query Docker Plugin]
    Query --> ListContainers[invoke list_containers]
    Query --> ListImages[invoke list_images]

    ListContainers --> Parse1[Parse docker ps -a]
    ListImages --> Parse2[Parse docker images]

    Parse1 --> Filter1[Filter by Query]
    Parse2 --> Filter2[Filter by Query]

    Filter1 --> Results1[Container Results]
    Filter2 --> Results2[Image Results]

    Results1 --> Render[Render Results]
    Results2 --> Render

    Render --> Select{User Selects?}
    Select -->|Container| ContainerAction{Action?}
    Select -->|Image| ImageAction[Delete Image]

    ContainerAction -->|Start| Start[invoke manage_container start]
    ContainerAction -->|Stop| Stop[invoke manage_container stop]
    ContainerAction -->|Restart| Restart[invoke manage_container restart]

    Start --> Refresh[Refresh List]
    Stop --> Refresh
    Restart --> Refresh
    ImageAction --> Refresh
    Refresh --> Query
```
